  "instructions": [
    "Combine flour, butter, and water in a bowl to form a dough.",
    "Roll out the dough to a thickness of 1/4 inch.",
    "Cut out circles of dough using a cookie cutter.",
    "Place 1 tablespoon of lardon-render on each dough circle.",
    "Fold the dough over the lardon-render to form a triangle.",
    "Press the edges to seal the pastry.",
    "Brush the tops of the pastry with egg wash.",
    "Place the tagines on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Bake in a preheated oven at 375°F for 20-25 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Dust with icing sugar before serving."
  ],
